"{\"uid\": \"independent.co.uk-sport-olympics-breaking-olympics-raygun-australia-paris-2024-bgirl-b2596742.html\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"Notifications can be managed in browser preferences.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 52, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Please refresh the page or navigate to another page on the site to be automatically logged inPlease refresh your browser to be logged in  Swipe for next article  An online petition has called for an investigation into Rachael Gunn's selection after her routine at Paris 2024 went viral  Removed from bookmarks  I would like to be emailed about offers, events and updates from The Independent.\", \"from\": 54, \"to\": 446, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 272, \"end\": 279, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rachael_Ray\", \"score\": 0.999996955042977, \"rank\": 3.0449630575221257e-06, \"text\": \"Rachael\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rachael_Ray\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rachael_Ray\"}, {\"begin\": 280, \"end\": 284, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Clan_Gunn\", \"score\": 0.99959156752506, \"rank\": 0.0003479630236709363, \"text\": \"Gunn\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Clan_Gunn\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Clan_Gunn\"}, {\"begin\": 318, \"end\": 328, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 0.999999999990905, \"rank\": 9.187380986286588e-12, \"text\": \"Paris 2024\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Read ourPrivacy notice  The Australian Olympic Committee (AOC) on Thursday condemned an online petition calling for an investigation intobreakdancer Rachael Gunn's selection forParis 2024, saying it contained falsehoods aimed at inciting hatred against her.\", \"from\": 447, \"to\": 704, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 471, \"end\": 485, \"