e/Anna_Meares\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The AOC has written to change.org demanding it take down the petition immediately, Carroll added.\", \"from\": 1527, \"to\": 1624, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1531, \"end\": 1534, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australian_Olympic_Committee\", \"score\": 0.7175257661598528, \"rank\": 0.39367817381193343, \"text\": \"AOC\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australian_Olympic_Committee\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australian_Olympic_Committee\"}, {\"begin\": 1610, \"end\": 1617, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/DeMarre_Carroll\", \"score\": 0.9990157238025628, \"rank\": 0.0004886548654271332, \"text\": \"Carroll\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q3665646\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/DeMarre_Carroll\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/DeMarre_Carroll\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Carroll also said that Gunn was selected through a transparent and independent qualification event and nomination process.\", \"from\": 1625, \"to\": 1747, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1625, \"end\": 1632, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/DeMarre_Carroll\", \"score\": 0.9990157238025628, \"rank\": 0.0004886548654271332, \"text\": \"Carroll\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q3665646\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/DeMarre_Carroll\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/DeMarre_Carroll\"}, {\"begin\": 1648, \"end\": 1652, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Clan_Gunn\", \"score\": 0.99959156752506, \"rank\": 0.0003479630236709363, \"text\": \"Gunn\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Clan_Gunn\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Clan_Gunn\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"The AOC is particularly offended by the affront to our Chef de Mission, Anna Meares,\\\" he added.\", \"from\": 1749, \"to\": 1845, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1754, \"end\": 1757, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/